{"tid":1262821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得咩新香港旗好鬼","createTime":"2019-06-28T01:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T02:00:49.000Z","uid":73057,"like":28,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"234e7ead5d99e653719c777feeeb28a6fdd3253e","tid":1262821,"uid":73057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuF6HbZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuF6HbZ.png&h=223ad5bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先個顏色已經出哂事<br />\n我地嘅文化，喪事先會夾呢兩隻色用<br />\n加埋代表香港嘅花<br />\n即係同香港送殯呀<br />\n<br />\n仲有，睇下d 藍屍post<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxRQ8Ui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxRQ8Ui.png&h=16c6574f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘩屌，呢兩隻色代表撐警<br />\n<br />\n個設計有種說不出的娘味，加埋隔離post 响旗桿嘅P 圖，相當可疑係大陸喱嘅手筆<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都知目的係要老屈抗爭者搞港獨<br />\n<br />\n大家呢次要意志堅定，目標明確<br />\n<br />\n撤回送中條例<br />\n釋放義士<br />\n追究警察監用武力"},{"pid":"7fcb65746f9567300bee91fc8f6b4ca40285642a","tid":1262821,"uid":142433,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:19:05.000Z","msg":"好野又有鬼捉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b833bc2e99ebf897da5056a3c405d75bd92de294","tid":1262821,"uid":52621,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:20:51.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n推黑旗好過 表達番香港將死/已死既訊息先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57b6608442a2df908d3a0971e0e6ac3fe0c5bc8","tid":1262821,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b833bc2e99ebf897da5056a3c405d75bd92de294","tid":1262821,"uid":52621,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:20:51.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n推黑旗好過 表達番香港將死/已死既訊息先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime